ecretKey` 泄露，以及提升鉴权配置文件的复用度，推荐配置 `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH` 鉴权 )\n- `0.0.20250420-2`:\n  - ✨ 支持透传 `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH` 里的 `userJwtToken`\n  - ✨ 支持通过 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 获取 JWT Token 后调用 MCP Server\n\n## 6. Luban\n\n- https://luban.bytedance.net/npm/publish/detail/8489/versions\n","name":"@byted/mcp-proxy","type":"module","exports":{".":{"types":"./dist/index.d.ts","import":"./dist/index.js","require":"./dist/index.cjs"}},"bin":{"mcp-proxy":"dist/index.js"}},"1.3.9":{"files":["dist"],"dependencies":{"zod":"^3.24.1","@byted-service/fetch":"^2.6.5","@byted/ai-paas-env":"^1.0.6","@byted/mcp-client-sdk":"^1.3.5-rc1","@modelcontextprotocol/sdk":"^1.0.3","jsonwebtoken":"^8.5.1"},"types":"./dist/index.d.ts","dist":{"fileCount":13,"shasum":"9ca671d7c4ae1e05cb47988f0d8fa9afb099cad9","integrity":"sha512-1lmPDEM2OOuP44p+3VPfKNPIZiWREfWzGd1rZwzLMx4SBdUjDS/TCWInNkxc/+9wLgMH0nutiJ8ejXT+gSjp5A==","tarball":"https://bnpm.byted.org/@byted/mcp-proxy/-/mcp-proxy-1.3.9.tgz","size":13375,"unpackedSize":77334},"name":"@byted/mcp-proxy","_npmUser":{"name":"baojinchang","email":"baojinchang@bytedance.com"},"module":"./dist/index.js","description":"## 0. Introduction","maintainers":[{"name":"yangyang.jeff","email":"yangyang.jeff@bytedance.com"},{"email":"mario7lorenzo@bytedance.com","name":"mario7lorenzo"},{"email":"wangnan.33@bytedance.com","name":"wangnan.33"},{"name":"baojinchang","email":"baojinchang@bytedance.com"}],"readmeFilename":"README.md","type":"module","_id":"@byted/mcp-proxy@1.3.9","devDependencies":{"prettier":"^3.5.3","@rslib/core":"^0.6.3","typescript-eslint":"^8.29.0","@types/jsonwebtoken":"^8.5.1","vitest":"^3.1.1","@eslint/js":"^9.27.0","@types/json-schema":"^7.0.15","globals":"^16.0.0","eslint":"^9.27.0","@vitest/coverage-v8":"3.1.1","@types/luxon":"^3.4.2","@types/estree":"^1.0.5","@biomejs/biome":"^1.9.4","ts-node":"^10.9.2","typescript":"^5.8.3","@types/node-fetch":"^2.6.11","shx":"^0.3.4","@types/node":"^22.8.1"},"version":"1.3.9","readme":"# @byted/mcp-proxy\n\n## 0. Introduction\n\n`@byted/mcp-proxy` 是一个用于将 ByteFaaS MCP Server 代理到本地的工具，适配各种第三方 MCP Client，如：\n\n- Trae (推荐)\n- Cursor\n- Windsurf\n- VS Code Cline\n\n## 1. Bnpm\n\n- https://bnpm.bytedance.net/package/@byted/mcp-proxy\n\n## 2. Precondition\n\n- 需要安装 Node.js v22 或更高版本。推荐使用 `nvm` 进行安装和管理：\n\n```bash\ncurl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.2/install.sh | bash\nnvm install 22 && nvm use 22 && nvm alias default 22\n```\n\n## 3. Config sample\n\n`@byted/mcp-proxy` 支持通过 4 种方案进行鉴权：\n\n- `bytefaas-cli` SSO 鉴权（个人账号的推荐方案）\n- 通过环境变量指定配置文件鉴权（服务账号的推荐方案）\n- 通过环境变量指定 `SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY` 鉴权\n- 通过环境变量指定 `USER_JWT_TOKEN` 鉴权\n\n### 3.1 `bytefaas-cli` SSO 鉴权\n\n配置 `@byted/mcp-proxy` 前，需要先下载 [bytefaas-cli](https://cloud.bytedance.net/docs/faas/docs/63d786117df7d2021dfc68e3/648a99992ca7dd02263c0d85) 并且完成登录:\n\n```shell\n# CN 或 BOE 区域登录命令\nAPP_ENV=production bytefaas login\n\n# I18N 区域登录命令\nAPP_ENV=i18n bytefaas login\n```\n\n获取 `bytefaas-cli` 登录态后，以当前用户个人账号身份使用 `@byted/mcp-proxy` 时，不再需要配置任何鉴权字段。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"--registry\", \"https://bnpm.byted.org\", \"-y\", \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.2 通过环境变量指定配置文件鉴权\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"--registry\", \"https://bnpm.byted.org\", \"-y\", \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH\": \"/Users/bytedance/myAuthenticationProfile.json\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n`authenticationProfile.json` 文件模板:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"serviceAccountSecretKey\": \"******\",\n  \"userJwtToken\": \"******\"\n}\n```\n\n注意：`serviceAccountSecretKey` 和 `userJwtToken` 不能同时被赋值。且由于 `userJwtToken` 存在过期机制，推荐使用 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 进行鉴权。\n\n### 3.3 通过环境变量指定 `SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY` 鉴权\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"--registry\", \"https://bnpm.byted.org\", \"-y\", \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY\": \"******\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.4 通过环境变量指定 `USER_JWT_TOKEN` 鉴权\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"--registry\", \"https://bnpm.byted.org\", \"-y\", \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"USER_JWT_TOKEN\": \"******\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.5 使用 `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_HEADERS` 指定 Call Tool 阶段的 Headers\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"--registry\", \"https://bnpm.byted.org\", \"-y\", \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_HEADERS\": \"key1=value1,key2=value2\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.6 使用 `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_COOKIES` 指定 Call Tool 阶段的 Cookies\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"--registry\", \"https://bnpm.byted.org\", \"-y\", \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_COOKIES\": \"cookie1=value1; cookie2=value2\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 4. Environment variables\n\n- `MCP_SERVER_PSM`：目标 MCP Server 的 PSM，必填。可以在 ByteFaaS 平台查看完整服务列表 [[Link](https://cloud.bytedance.net/faas/mcp_servers?x-resource-account=public&x-bc-region-id=bytedance)]\n- `MCP_GATEWAY_REGION`：MCP Gateway 的区域，必填，可选值：`BOE`、`CN`、`I18N`\n- `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`：鉴权配置文件路径，选填。`AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`、`SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`、`USER_JWT_TOKEN` 最多只能赋值 1 个，如果都不赋值，`@byted/mcp-proxy` 将不会携带鉴权信息访问 MCP Server。\n- `SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`: 服务账号 SecretKey，选填。`AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`、`SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`、`USER_JWT_TOKEN` 最多只能赋值 1 个，如果都不赋值，`@byted/mcp-proxy` 将不会携带鉴权信息访问 MCP Server。\n- `USER_JWT_TOKEN`: 用户 JWT Token，选填。`AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`、`SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`、`USER_JWT_TOKEN` 最多只能赋值 1 个，如果都不赋值，`@byted/mcp-proxy` 将不会携带鉴权信息访问 MCP Server。\n- `MCP_REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS`: 配置 MCP 请求的超时时间，默认超时时间为 60 秒\n- `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_HEADERS`: 指定 Call Tool 阶段的 Headers，例如：key1=value1,key2=value2\n- `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_PARAMS`: 指定 Call Tool 阶段的 Params，例如：param1=value1,param2=value2\n- `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_WITH_COOKIES`: 是否在 Call Tool 阶段透传字节云的 Cookie，默认为 false\n- `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_COOKIES`: 指定 Call Tool 阶段的 Cookies，例如：cookie1=value1; cookie2=value2\n- `MCP_SERVER_TOOL_BLOCK_LIST`: MCP Server 提供的 Tool list 黑名单\n- `MCP_SERVER_TOOL_ALLOW_LIST`: MCP Server 提供的 Tool list 白名单\n- `LOG_LEVEL`: MCP Proxy 日志级别，可选值：`trace`、`debug`、`info`、`warn`、`error`，默认值：`info`\n- `MCP_SERVER_ENV`: MCP Server 的环境，选填。如果指定了环境，`@byted/mcp-proxy` 将在请求 MCP Server 时，添加 `env` 参数。\n\n\n## 5. Change log\n\n- `1.3.9`\n  - 🏗 支持通过`MCP_SERVER_ENV`环境变量访问mcp ppe环境\n- `1.3.4`:\n  - 🏗 集成 `@byted/ai-paas-env`\n  - 🐛 修复 `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_COOKIES` 未成功透传 Cookie 的问题\n  - 🐛 修复 Non-TT 域名拉闸导致的 I18N MCP 网关域名访问不了的问题\n- `1.2.3`:\n  - ✨ 支持通过环境变量 `LOG_LEVEL` 指定日志级别\n  - 🏗 升级 `@byted/mcp-client-sdk` 依赖版本到 `1.1.1`\n- `1.1.0`:\n  - ✨ 支持通过环境变量 `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_COOKIES` 指定 Call Tool 阶段的 Cookies\n- `1.0.0`:\n  - 🏗 发布正式版本\n- `0.0.20250701-1`:\n  - 🏗 修改通过 Tiktok SSO 获取 JWT 的超时时间为 10 秒\n- `0.0.20250618-1`:\n  - 🏗 修改通过 Service account secret key 获取 JWT 的超时时间为 10 秒\n- `0.0.20250609-1`:\n  - ✨ 当 `bytefaas-cli` 登录态过期后，在 Init 阶段的日志里提示用户重新登录\n- `0.0.20250528-1`:\n  - ✨ 支持通过环境变量 `MCP_SERVER_TOOL_BLOCK_LIST` 和 `MCP_SERVER_TOOL_ALLOW_LIST` 对 MCP Server 提供的 Tool list 进行限制\n- `0.0.20250523-2`:\n  - ✨ 支持通过环境变量 `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_WITH_COOKIES` 指定，是否在 Call Tool 阶段透传字节云的 Cookie\n- `0.0.20250521-4`:\n  - 🏗 升级 `@byted/mcp-client-sdk` 依赖版本到 `0.0.20250521-2`\n  - 🏗 强制指定网络环境为办公网\n  - 🏗 标准化日志输出\n  - 🏗 修改默认超时时间为 60 秒\n  - 🏗 在 MCP Server Init 阶段提前执行一次 `listToolsHandler` ，以便将 List Tool 阶段的 401 错误提前暴露\n- `0.0.20250520-1`:\n  - ✨ 支持通过环境变量 `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_HEADERS` 和 `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_PARAMS` 指定 Call Tool 阶段的 Headers 和 Params\n- `0.0.20250507-1`:\n  - 🏗 升级 `@byted/mcp-client-sdk` 依赖版本到 `0.0.20250430-1`\n  - 🐛 修复 I18N 区域无法通过 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 获取 JWT 的问题\n- `0.0.20250428-3`:\n  - 🏗 当 `BytedMcpClient.loadAllTools` 失败时，捕获异常并且打印日志\n  - ✨ 支持 I18N 区域的 MCP Server 自动从 [bytefaas-cli](https://cloud.bytedance.net/docs/faas/docs/63d786117df7d2021dfc68e3/648a99992ca7dd02263c0d85) 的 SSO 数据里获取 JWT Token (不再需要显式指定`USER_JWT_TOKEN`)，通过 `APP_ENV=i18n bytefaas login` 登录后，登录态可以最长可以维持 1 个月\n- `0.0.20250427-2`:\n  - 🏗 在通过任意方式获取 JWT 后，进行 auth 验证，拦截无效的 JWT，并且打印有效 JWT 的身份信息\n  - ✨ 支持 CN 和 BOE 区域的 MCP Server 自动从 [bytefaas-cli](https://cloud.bytedance.net/docs/faas/docs/63d786117df7d2021dfc68e3/648a99992ca7dd02263c0d85) 的 SSO 数据里获取 JWT Token (不再需要显式指定`USER_JWT_TOKEN`)，通过 `APP_ENV=production bytefaas login` 登录后，登录态可以最长可以维持 1 年\n- `0.0.20250425-2`:\n  - 🏗 打印 Call Tool 阶段的 Request Header, Request Body, Response Body\n  - ✨ 支持通过环境变量 `MCP_REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS` 配置 MCP 请求的超时时间，默认超时时间为 10 秒\n- `0.0.20250424-1`:\n  - 🏗 升级 `@byted/mcp-client-sdk` 依赖版本到 `0.0.20250423-1`\n- `0.0.20250422-2`:\n  - 🏗 升级 `@byted/mcp-client-sdk` 依赖版本到 `0.0.20250421-6`\n  - ✨ 支持每 30 分钟更新由 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 生成的 JWT Token\n  - ✨ 支持在环境变量中直接指定 `SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY` 和 `USER_JWT_TOKEN` (不过，为了避免 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 泄露，以及提升鉴权配置文件的复用度，推荐配置 `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH` 鉴权 )\n- `0.0.20250420-2`:\n  - ✨ 支持透传 `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH` 里的 `userJwtToken`\n  - ✨ 支持通过 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 获取 JWT Token 后调用 MCP Server\n\n## 6. Luban\n\n- https://luban.bytedance.net/npm/publish/detail/8489/versions\n","main":"./dist/index.cjs","license":"MIT","exports":{".":{"types":"./dist/index.d.ts","import":"./dist/index.js","require":"./dist/index.cjs"}},"scripts":{"dev":"rslib build --watch","format":"prettier --write .","lint":"eslint .","test":"vitest run","test:cov":"vitest run --coverage","playground":"ts-node __test__/playground.ts","build":"rslib build && yarn test:cov","check":"biome check --write"},"bin":{"mcp-proxy":"dist/index.js"}},"0.0.20250422-2":{"exports":{".":{"require":"./dist/index.cjs","types":"./dist/index.d.ts","import":"./dist/index.js"}},"type":"module","module":"./dist/index.js","maintainers":[{"email":"yangyang.jeff@bytedance.com","name":"yangyang.jeff"}],"name":"@byted/mcp-proxy","description":"## Introduction `@byted/mcp-proxy` 是一个用于将 ByteFaaS MCP Server 代理到本地的工具，适配各种第三方 MCP Client，如： - Cursor - Windsurf - VS Code Cline","readmeFilename":"README.md","readme":"# @byted/mcp-proxy\n\n## Introduction\n`@byted/mcp-proxy` 是一个用于将 ByteFaaS MCP Server 代理到本地的工具，适配各种第三方 MCP Client，如：\n- Cursor\n- Windsurf\n- VS Code Cline\n\n## Bnpm\n- https://bnpm.bytedance.net/package/@byted/mcp-proxy\n\n## Precondition\n\n- 需要安装 Node.js v22 或更高版本。推荐使用 `nvm` 进行安装和管理：\n\n```bash\ncurl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.2/install.sh | bash\nnvm install 22 && nvm use 22\n```\n\n## Code sample\n通过配置文件鉴权（推荐）\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"--registry\",\n        \"https://bnpm.byted.org\",\n        \"-y\",\n        \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"\n      ],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH\": \"/Users/bytedance/myAuthenticationProfile.json\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n通过服务账号 SecretKey 鉴权\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"--registry\",\n        \"https://bnpm.byted.org\",\n        \"-y\",\n        \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"\n      ],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY\": \"******\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n通过用户 JWT Token 鉴权\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\n        \"--registry\",\n        \"https://bnpm.byted.org\",\n        \"-y\",\n        \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"\n      ],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"USER_JWT_TOKEN\": \"******\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Environment variables\n- `MCP_SERVER_PSM`：目标 MCP Server 的 PSM，必填。可以在 ByteFaaS 平台查看完整服务列表 [[Link](https://cloud.bytedance.net/faas/mcp_servers?x-resource-account=public&x-bc-region-id=bytedance)]\n- `MCP_GATEWAY_REGION`：MCP Gateway 的区域，必填，可选值：`BOE`、`CN`、`I18N`\n- `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`：鉴权配置文件路径，选填。`AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`、`SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`、`USER_JWT_TOKEN` 最多只能赋值 1 个，如果都不赋值，`@byted/mcp-proxy` 将不会携带鉴权信息访问 MCP Server。\n- `SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`: 服务账号 SecretKey，选填。`AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`、`SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`、`USER_JWT_TOKEN` 最多只能赋值 1 个，如果都不赋值，`@byted/mcp-proxy` 将不会携带鉴权信息访问 MCP Server。\n- `USER_JWT_TOKEN`: 用户 JWT Token，选填。`AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`、`SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`、`USER_JWT_TOKEN` 最多只能赋值 1 个，如果都不赋值，`@byted/mcp-proxy` 将不会携带鉴权信息访问 MCP Server。\n\n### AuthenticationProfile definition\n`authenticationProfile.json` 文件模板: \n\n```json\n{\n  \"serviceAccountSecretKey\": \"******\",\n  \"userJwtToken\": \"******\"\n}\n```\n\n注意：`serviceAccountSecretKey` 和 `userJwtToken` 不能同时被赋值。且由于 `userJwtToken` 存在过期机制，推荐使用 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 进行鉴权。\n\n## Change log\n\n- `0.0.20250422-2`:\n  - 升级 `@byted/mcp-client-sdk` 依赖版本到 `0.0.20250421-6`\n  - 支持每 30 分钟更新由 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 生成的 JWT Token\n  - 支持在环境变量中直接指定 `SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY` 和 `USER_JWT_TOKEN` (不过，为了避免 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 泄露，以及提升鉴权配置文件的复用度，推荐配置 `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH` 鉴权 )\n- `0.0.20250420-2`: \n  - 支持透传 `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH` 里的 `userJwtToken`\n  - 支持通过 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 获取 JWT Token 后调用 MCP Server\n\n## Luban\n- https://luban.bytedance.net/npm/publish/detail/8489/versions\n","main":"./dist/index.cjs","_id":"@byted/mcp-proxy@0.0.20250422-2","files":["dist"],"bin":{"mcp-proxy":"dist/index.js"},"devDependencies":{"@eslint/js":"^9.23.0","typescript":"^5.8.3","globals":"^16.0.0","eslint":"^9.23.0","@biomejs/biome":"^1.9.4","@types/node":"^22.8.1","@rslib/core":"^0.6.3","vitest":"^3.1.1","shx":"^0.3.4","prettier":"^3.5.3","typescript-eslint":"^8.29.0"},"version":"0.0.20250422-2","types":"./dist/index.d.ts","dependencies":{"zod":"^3.24.1","@modelcontextprotocol/sdk":"^1.0.3","@byted/mcp-client-sdk":"0.0.20250421-6"},"dist":{"fileCount":6,"shasum":"ce8a94fcf65523602c32dd91cd3df8c08951fe8f","integrity":"sha512-QNNReTnHy2xzFJL62V23lFUkAz8GaSSUOgF4UTCT1EVBvMR9qlFw/6t2njfAzWLMOhlgBANikOLWLFQdARBQYQ==","tarball":"https://bnpm.byted.org/@byted/mcp-proxy/-/mcp-proxy-0.0.20250422-2.tgz","size":5898,"unpackedSize":32405},"_npmUser":{"name":"yangyang.jeff","email":"yangyang.jeff@bytedance.com"},"scripts":{"format":"prettier --write .","lint":"eslint .","test":"vitest run","build":"rslib build","check":"biome check --write","dev":"rslib build --watch"}},"0.0.20250609-1":{"scripts":{"test":"vitest run","playground":"ts-node __test__/playground.ts","build":"rslib build","check":"biome check --write","dev":"rslib build --watch","format":"prettier --write .","lint":"eslint ."},"readmeFilename":"README.md","maintainers":[{"email":"yangyang.jeff@bytedance.com","name":"yangyang.jeff"}],"bin":{"mcp-proxy":"dist/index.js"},"devDependencies":{"ts-node":"^10.9.2","@types/jsonwebtoken":"^8.5.1","typescript":"^5.8.3","eslint":"^9.27.0","@types/node":"^22.8.1","shx":"^0.3.4","globals":"^16.0.0","vitest":"^3.1.1","typescript-eslint":"^8.29.0","prettier":"^3.5.3","@rslib/core":"^0.6.3","@eslint/js":"^9.27.0","@biomejs/biome":"^1.9.4"},"_id":"@byted/mcp-proxy@0.0.20250609-1","exports":{".":{"import":"./dist/index.js","require":"./dist/index.cjs","types":"./dist/index.d.ts"}},"module":"./dist/index.js","_npmUser":{"name":"yangyang.jeff","email":"yangyang.jeff@bytedance.com"},"readme":"# @byted/mcp-proxy\n\n## 0. Introduction\n\n`@byted/mcp-proxy` 是一个用于将 ByteFaaS MCP Server 代理到本地的工具，适配各种第三方 MCP Client，如：\n\n- Trae (推荐)\n- Cursor\n- Windsurf\n- VS Code Cline\n\n## 1. Bnpm\n\n- https://bnpm.bytedance.net/package/@byted/mcp-proxy\n\n## 2. Precondition\n\n- 需要安装 Node.js v22 或更高版本。推荐使用 `nvm` 进行安装和管理：\n\n```bash\ncurl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.2/install.sh | bash\nnvm install 22 && nvm use 22 && nvm alias default 22\n```\n\n## 3. Config sample\n\n`@byted/mcp-proxy` 支持通过 4 种方案进行鉴权：\n\n- `bytefaas-cli` SSO 鉴权（个人账号的推荐方案）\n- 通过环境变量指定配置文件鉴权（服务账号的推荐方案）\n- 通过环境变量指定 `SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY` 鉴权\n- 通过环境变量指定 `USER_JWT_TOKEN` 鉴权\n\n### 3.1 `bytefaas-cli` SSO 鉴权\n\n配置 `@byted/mcp-proxy` 前，需要先下载 [bytefaas-cli](https://cloud.bytedance.net/docs/faas/docs/63d786117df7d2021dfc68e3/648a99992ca7dd02263c0d85) 并且完成登录:\n\n```shell\n# CN or BOE 区域登录命令\nAPP_ENV=production bytefaas login\n\n# I18N 区域登录命令\nAPP_ENV=i18n bytefaas login\n```\n\n获取 `bytefaas-cli` 登录态后，以当前用户个人账号身份使用 `@byted/mcp-proxy` 时，不再需要配置任何鉴权字段。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"--registry\", \"https://bnpm.byted.org\", \"-y\", \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.2 通过环境变量指定配置文件鉴权\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"--registry\", \"https://bnpm.byted.org\", \"-y\", \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH\": \"/Users/bytedance/myAuthenticationProfile.json\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n`authenticationProfile.json` 文件模板:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"serviceAccountSecretKey\": \"******\",\n  \"userJwtToken\": \"******\"\n}\n```\n\n注意：`serviceAccountSecretKey` 和 `userJwtToken` 不能同时被赋值。且由于 `userJwtToken` 存在过期机制，推荐使用 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 进行鉴权。\n\n### 3.3 通过环境变量指定 `SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY` 鉴权\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"--registry\", \"https://bnpm.byted.org\", \"-y\", \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY\": \"******\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3.4 通过环境变量指定 `USER_JWT_TOKEN` 鉴权\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"mcp-server-sample\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"--registry\", \"https://bnpm.byted.org\", \"-y\", \"@byted/mcp-proxy@latest\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"MCP_SERVER_PSM\": \"inf.sinf.sample_mcp\",\n        \"MCP_GATEWAY_REGION\": \"CN\",\n        \"USER_JWT_TOKEN\": \"******\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 4. Environment variables\n\n- `MCP_SERVER_PSM`：目标 MCP Server 的 PSM，必填。可以在 ByteFaaS 平台查看完整服务列表 [[Link](https://cloud.bytedance.net/faas/mcp_servers?x-resource-account=public&x-bc-region-id=bytedance)]\n- `MCP_GATEWAY_REGION`：MCP Gateway 的区域，必填，可选值：`BOE`、`CN`、`I18N`\n- `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`：鉴权配置文件路径，选填。`AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`、`SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`、`USER_JWT_TOKEN` 最多只能赋值 1 个，如果都不赋值，`@byted/mcp-proxy` 将不会携带鉴权信息访问 MCP Server。\n- `SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`: 服务账号 SecretKey，选填。`AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`、`SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`、`USER_JWT_TOKEN` 最多只能赋值 1 个，如果都不赋值，`@byted/mcp-proxy` 将不会携带鉴权信息访问 MCP Server。\n- `USER_JWT_TOKEN`: 用户 JWT Token，选填。`AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH`、`SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY`、`USER_JWT_TOKEN` 最多只能赋值 1 个，如果都不赋值，`@byted/mcp-proxy` 将不会携带鉴权信息访问 MCP Server。\n- `MCP_REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS`: 配置 MCP 请求的超时时间，默认超时时间为 60 秒\n- `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_HEADERS`: 指定 Call Tool 阶段的 Headers\n- `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_PARAMS`: 指定 Call Tool 阶段的 Params\n- `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_WITH_COOKIES`: 是否在 Call Tool 阶段透传字节云的 Cookie，默认为 false\n- `MCP_SERVER_TOOL_BLOCK_LIST`: MCP Server 提供的 Tool list 黑名单\n- `MCP_SERVER_TOOL_ALLOW_LIST`: MCP Server 提供的 Tool list 白名单\n\n\n## 5. Change log\n\n- `0.0.20250609-1`:\n  - ✨ 当 `bytefaas-cli` 登录态过期后，在 Init 阶段的日志里提示用户重新登录\n- `0.0.20250528-1`:\n  - ✨ 支持通过环境变量 `MCP_SERVER_TOOL_BLOCK_LIST` 和 `MCP_SERVER_TOOL_ALLOW_LIST` 对 MCP Server 提供的 Tool list 进行限制\n- `0.0.20250523-2`:\n  - ✨ 支持通过环境变量 `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_WITH_COOKIES` 指定，是否在 Call Tool 阶段透传字节云的 Cookie\n- `0.0.20250521-4`:\n  - 🏗 升级 `@byted/mcp-client-sdk` 依赖版本到 `0.0.20250521-2`\n  - 🏗 强制指定网络环境为办公网\n  - 🏗 标准化日志输出\n  - 🏗 修改默认超时时间为 60 秒\n  - 🏗 在 MCP Server Init 阶段提前执行一次 `listToolsHandler` ，以便将 List Tool 阶段的 401 错误提前暴露\n- `0.0.20250520-1`:\n  - ✨ 支持通过环境变量 `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_HEADERS` 和 `MCP_SERVER_CALL_TOOL_PARAMS` 指定 Call Tool 阶段的 Headers 和 Params\n- `0.0.20250507-1`:\n  - 🏗 升级 `@byted/mcp-client-sdk` 依赖版本到 `0.0.20250430-1`\n  - 🐛 修复 I18N 区域无法通过 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 获取 JWT 的问题\n- `0.0.20250428-3`:\n  - 🏗 当 `BytedMcpClient.loadAllTools` 失败时，捕获异常并且打印日志\n  - ✨ 支持 I18N 区域的 MCP Server 自动从 [bytefaas-cli](https://cloud.bytedance.net/docs/faas/docs/63d786117df7d2021dfc68e3/648a99992ca7dd02263c0d85) 的 SSO 数据里获取 JWT Token (不再需要显式指定`USER_JWT_TOKEN`)，通过 `APP_ENV=i18n bytefaas login` 登录后，登录态可以最长可以维持 1 个月\n- `0.0.20250427-2`:\n  - 🏗 在通过任意方式获取 JWT 后，进行 auth 验证，拦截无效的 JWT，并且打印有效 JWT 的身份信息\n  - ✨ 支持 CN 和 BOE 区域的 MCP Server 自动从 [bytefaas-cli](https://cloud.bytedance.net/docs/faas/docs/63d786117df7d2021dfc68e3/648a99992ca7dd02263c0d85) 的 SSO 数据里获取 JWT Token (不再需要显式指定`USER_JWT_TOKEN`)，通过 `APP_ENV=production bytefaas login` 登录后，登录态可以最长可以维持 1 年\n- `0.0.20250425-2`:\n  - 🏗 打印 Call Tool 阶段的 Request Header, Request Body, Response Body\n  - ✨ 支持通过环境变量 `MCP_REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS` 配置 MCP 请求的超时时间，默认超时时间为 10 秒\n- `0.0.20250424-1`:\n  - 🏗 升级 `@byted/mcp-client-sdk` 依赖版本到 `0.0.20250423-1`\n- `0.0.20250422-2`:\n  - 🏗 升级 `@byted/mcp-client-sdk` 依赖版本到 `0.0.20250421-6`\n  - ✨ 支持每 30 分钟更新由 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 生成的 JWT Token\n  - ✨ 支持在环境变量中直接指定 `SERVICE_ACCOUNT_SECRET_KEY` 和 `USER_JWT_TOKEN` (不过，为了避免 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 泄露，以及提升鉴权配置文件的复用度，推荐配置 `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH` 鉴权 )\n- `0.0.20250420-2`:\n  - ✨ 支持透传 `AUTHENTICATION_PROFILE_PATH` 里的 `userJwtToken`\n  - ✨ 支持通过 `serviceAccountSecretKey` 获取 JWT Token 后调用 MCP Server\n\n## 6. Luban\n\n- https://luban.bytedance.net/npm/publish/detail/8489/versions\n","main":"./dist/index.cjs","license":"MIT","files":["dist"],"version":"0.0.20250609-1","type":"module","dist":{"size":10915,"unpackedSize":66232,"fileCount":8,"shasum":"c0d38d1b5c39868bd1d9b6eb71215ae50b1058bc","integrity":"sha512-XcUMCMBQf/CRJ+mDdTQSWumFOHrLpxJMGwKh0etRHjmBq2HROjni7YIRxMyj+y0Ah9mu6F3ii0tIpEZ6RUTk4A==","tarball":"https://bnpm.byted.org/@byted/mcp-proxy/-/mcp-proxy-0.0.20250609-1.tgz"},"dependencies":{"@modelcontextprotocol/sdk":"^1.0.3","@byted/mcp-client-sdk":"0.0.20250521-2","jsonwebtoken":"^8.5.1","@byted-service/fetch":"^2.6.5","zod":"^3.24.1"},"types":"./dist/index.d.ts","description":"## 0. Introduction","name":"@byted/mcp-proxy"},"0.0.20250417-3":{"description":"https://bnpm.bytedance.net/package/@byted/mcp-proxy","maintainers":[{"email":"yangyang.jeff@bytedance.com","name":"yangyang.jeff"}],"_npmUser":{"email":"yangyang.jeff@bytedance.com","name":"yangyang.jeff"},"module":"./dist/index.js","readmeFilename":"README.md","exports":{".":{"import":"./dist/index.js","require":"./dist/index.cjs","types"